ygData.messageBody:
Hello Ladies =)
My name is Lori and i have bene playing EverQuest for over 4 years
now. I am on The Nameless. I have my main char. Named Lorina
(Cleric) lvl 51., Lorinya (Beastlord) 24, Lori (Druid) lvl 25,
Loriana (warrior) lvl 26, and a few lower lvls as well. (Yes i am
stuck on the Lori names, LOL. No chars have Epics, and i am getting
the tch to get my clerics really badly. So we will see.
I Just came across this board yesterday And wanted to give an
introduction. If anyone sees me in world give me a tell, let me know
you saw me on the board =)
Have fun!
~Lori
